title: Chiefs talk with Brooke Pryor (Football 6/25)
description:
Will Brinson breaks down the latest news and notes from around the NFL and then is joined by Brooke Pryor of the Kansas City Star to talk about the Tyreek Hill situation, the Chiefs offseason and what to look forward to in the coming season from the offense and defense.
